## Current Migration Goal

Move incrementally from Zustand persisted local storage to:

```
Clerk user
    |
Next.js backend (Route Handlers / server actions)
    |
Prisma ORM
    |
PostgreSQL
```

Migrate one domain at a time (e.g. profile ‚Üí problems ‚Üí notes). Keep the UI working at each step.

